news.news_title: NASA's Mars 2020 Rover Does Biceps Curls
news.news_text: In this time-lapse video, the robotic arm on NASA's Mars 2020 rover maneuvers its 88-pound (40-kilogram) sensor-laden turret as it moves from a deployed to stowed configuration.
